data.title: Arnold Schwarzenegger Biography
data.meta_description: Read all about Arnold Schwarzenegger with TV Guide's exclusive biography including their list of awards, celeb facts and more at TV Guide.
data.text:
Fast Facts

Was a soldier in the Austrian Army, 1965-66

Came to America in 1968 and became a citizen in 1983

Was a millionaire before the age of 22 due to his business investments, which included real estate and a bodybuilding-equipment company

Won the title of Mr

Olympia seven times and Mr

Universe three times; also won Junior Mr

Europe and Mr

World

Screen acting debut was in 1970's Hercules in New York (billed as Arnold Strong)

Was a contestant on The Dating Game in 1972

Modeled for Andy Warhol

Although Republican, he married Democratic Kennedy clan member Maria Shriver in 1986

Became the 38th governor of California on November 17, 2003
